</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check whether clean media is used.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Clean the media using IPA or cut the polluted part of the media.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check whether the used media is white.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">This calibration can only be executed on white and smooth media.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check whether the M&amp;C-scanner needs to be cleaned.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Clean the glass-window of the M&amp;C-scanner using IPA.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Desicion
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check whether the printed pattern look complete (no deviation droplets).
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">See example top of this page.
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Perform manual maintenance on the printheads.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check the M&amp;C-scanner.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref href="GUID-17F448B7-8A72-45B1-B56D-FC5C0BE28701.xml" class="- topic/xref " type="task"><?ditaot gentext?>05-6-017 M&amp;C scanner test [Special Tests]</xref>
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">10 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Replace the printhead.
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref href="GUID-915F84BE-7881-400A-A351-FF4DB79FE9B0" class="- topic/xref "/>
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11 
